displayProperties.name: Thrilladrome
displayProperties.description: Sam Moleyn says they have a thing called "Skee-Ball," and with enough points, you can win prizes. Ghost really wants to come back when things "calm down."

displayProperties.name: Hydroponics Delta
displayProperties.description: The Shadow Legion have broken into critical hydroponics infrastructure, a production centre for Neomuni food supply. Secure the facility.

displayProperties.name: Gilded Precept
displayProperties.description:
"What is the Earth idiom? Through a... mirror?"
Forbidden tradition. The Shadow Legion want to fight, so fight them.

displayProperties.name: Garden of Salvation
displayProperties.description: The Garden calls out to you. It offers "Salvation" but at what cost... Silence the signal.
